content.Mon4: I've learned a lot from my parrot family...#$b#But I'm sure there's a lot more out there I don't know.$s
content.Tue: When Sun is angry, it feels good in the jungle.#$e#Sun can't find us beneath the leaves. We trick him! Haha...$h
content.Wed2: Be careful in the volcano... the spirits don't like outsiders.
content.Thu: Have you met the others like you?#$b#I don't talk to them much. I feel safer with my own kind...$3
content.Fri: One time... I was at the top of the volcano at night, and I saw lights far, far away.#$b#I wonder if there are other bird families out there?$3
content.Fri3: I wonder if I could see your home from the top of the volcano?
content.Sat: ...I'm sad today.$s#$e#You go on... have fun. Let me be sad.$s
content.Sun: When it rains, strange birds visit.#$b#I try to speak to them... but they fly away.$s#$b#I guess they don't want to be friends...$s
